---
title: BPMN-style flow — Daily Sales Aggregation (Spec §10.1)
---
flowchart LR
    start([⏱ Cron 02:00 UTC]):::evt
    job[Spring Batch Job: dailySalesJob]:::task
    read[Read bookings WHERE created_at::date = yesterday<br/>OR cancelled_at::date = yesterday]:::task
    proc[Aggregate by event_id<br/>tickets_sold / tickets_cancelled / revenue / refunds]:::task
    write[UPSERT analytics.event_daily_sales<br/>ON CONFLICT event_id, sales_date]:::task
    decision{rows committed?}:::gw
    ok([✅ End]):::evt
    retry[Spring Batch retry from last commit]:::task
    err([❌ Job FAILED — alert]):::evt

    start --> job --> read --> proc --> write --> decision
    decision -->|yes| ok
    decision -->|no, transient| retry --> read
    decision -->|no, fatal| err

    classDef evt fill:#fff5d6,stroke:#b58900;
    classDef task fill:#e0f0ff,stroke:#268bd2;
    classDef gw fill:#f0e0ff,stroke:#6c71c4;
